# Project Standards for "Мягкие окна СПб"

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15+ (App Router)
- TypeScript (Strict mode)
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Shadcn/UI for components
- Lucide-react for icons

## Coding Rules
- Use Functional Components and Hooks (no Classes).
- Favor Server Components for SEO and speed.
- All styling must be done via Tailwind CSS.
- Ensure 100% Mobile-first responsiveness.
- Use `next/image` for all images with appropriate `sizes` and `priority` for LCP.

## SEO & Accessibility
- Maintain semantic HTML (header, main, section, footer).
- Strictly one <h1> per page.
- All interactive elements must have aria-labels.
- Implement JSON-LD (Schema.org) for LocalBusiness.

## Vibe Coding Instructions
- Always refer to `design-reference.png` for visual style, colors, and spacing.
- If the design is unclear, ask for clarification before coding.
- Keep the code clean and avoid "magic numbers" in CSS.